{"tid":983764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"漁護署倡清理廚餘減野豬　梁振英：哪野豬一家大小吃什麼？","createTime":"2019-01-16T08:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T18:23:01.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"06eb81a782c46a7f68a23f0eb0f503048cdc9a1e","tid":983764,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T08:42:36.000Z","msg":"野豬問題近日成為政圈熱話，前特首梁振英亦加入戰陣討論，日前在其facebook專頁發帖，圖文並茂指出其住所附近經常出現野豬的蹤跡，質疑「野狗野貓會被人道毀滅，老鼠和曱甴會被毒殺，野豬為什麼有不同待遇」?<br />\n<br />\nCY今日繼續狙擊野豬問題，不過立場似一百八十度轉變，反對漁農署以清理廚餘減少野豬數目的計劃，批評：「平白餓死野豬，人道嗎？」又指肚餓的野豬，攻擊人的可能性更大。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2327848/org/a7e5915c99b7a54766cee6b735190484.jpg/MNjLoDMazA0lf4y7vY5Pz2h0dTiags8410g-w9dIPsM?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2327848%2Forg%2Fa7e5915c99b7a54766cee6b735190484.jpg%2FMNjLoDMazA0lf4y7vY5Pz2h0dTiags8410g-w9dIPsM%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=446029e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">梁振英日前上傳一張不知道是否由他拍攝，野豬在垃圾桶尋食的照片，未知是否想對野豬問題反映不滿。(梁振英fb)</span><br />\n<br />\n事隔短短幾日，梁振英再度「出擊」，但今次的「箭靶」不是野豬，而是漁農署。他首先提到東區區議會今日開會討論野豬管理行動，漁護署人員在會上說，大多數野豬滋擾事件源於覓食。梁振英筆鋒一轉，說野豬食量大，在郊野公園一帶沒有足够的天然食物，因此吃垃圾裡的厨餘。他問道：「垃圾桶和垃圾站管理好了，野豬不能吃垃圾裡的廚餘，哪野豬一家大小吃什麼？」<br />\n<br />\n梁振英意猶未盡，續追問：「平白餓死野豬，人道嗎？肚餓的野豬，攻擊人的可能性更大。」看來CY確實很關心野豬一家大小的「伙食」問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/283284/%E6%BC%81%E8%AD%B7%E7%BD%B2%E5%80%A1%E6%B8%85%E7%90%86%E5%BB%9A%E9%A4%98%E6%B8%9B%E9%87%8E%E8%B1%AC-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1-%E5%93%AA%E9%87%8E%E8%B1%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%90%83%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F283284%2F%25E6%25BC%2581%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25BB%259A%25E9%25A4%2598%25E6%25B8%259B%25E9%2587%258E%25E8%25B1%25AC-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1-%25E5%2593%25AA%25E9%2587%258E%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%2590%2583%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC&d=ve7y2Oq%2Bf%2BwNP8CnQWAq8DPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b2356386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/283284/%E6%BC%81%E8%AD%B7%E7%BD%B2%E5%80%A1%E6%B8%85%E7%90%86%E5%BB%9A%E9%A4%98%E6%B8%9B%E9%87%8E%E8%B1%AC-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1-%E5%93%AA%E9%87%8E%E8%B1%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%90%83%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC</a>"},{"pid":"9b4b409c39c76601c98eadb6a873e58c4f9317eb","tid":983764,"uid":19557,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T08:45:41.000Z","msg":"痴筋 一時就話野豬要人道委滅 一時就好關心野豬一家到時食乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e64acd07f9d3d9f84e3197587f48aba4a98137e","tid":983764,"uid":53687,"like":46,"dislike":3,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:08:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">肚餓的野豬，攻擊人的可能性更大。</span><br />\n<br />\n咁呢句其實又錯唔晒"},{"pid":"93b5ceb26904a48b188695e0f1d7b6052b7a179a","tid":983764,"uid":105879,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:09:53.000Z","msg":"佢驚肚餓既野豬直接沖入佢屋企咋on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bdbf1ed7b984f927dea323bc17ec63745384ef6","tid":983764,"uid":99962,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:11:21.000Z","msg":"梁生突然咁好心分分鐘有陰毛<br />\n<br />\n想翻閹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc445a776e4d514d5472c37511e74e16dc96d49a","tid":983764,"uid":68556,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T09:12:47.000Z","msg":"綜合而睇， 佢應該係支持直接殺晒野豬全家，<br />\n而唔好搞d咩減少廚餘依d間接方法。<br />\n<br />\n其實無衝突嘅。"},{"pid":"86161d99bed0bca91d0bf85e4f429dd479376eb1","tid":983764,"uid":28279,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01